應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUis%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=6f0b8602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56d103ea834c78cf88bb90fa37df137df3fb9c3","tid":1518183,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:23.000Z","msg":"大家都好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46447e4b6fea5ab554ef7eb4c695c0a902b33348","tid":1518183,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}